{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spectral Prison is a horror game where you are stuck in a loop in a house that seems to change at the whims of a sinister Warden out to make sure you can never get out.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Trapped\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">David Echo wakes in a dimly lit bedroom, the only familiar place in a house that feels eerily distorted. Your goal? Find the keys to unlock the doors and escape this spectral prison. But beware, the house is filled with terrifying surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Think you've finally escaped? Think again. A sinister warden watches your every move, ready to capture you and send you to an even more terrifying dimension.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Warden's Wrath</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The warden does not like you beating his games and will try to make every loop harder, trying to make you quit and stay in his prison.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260000/extras/Spectral_Prison_Wardens_Wrath.gif?t=1737062827\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Ever changing house</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every time you return, the house alters itself. Key positions change as the warden tries to keep you locked in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260000/extras/EverChangingHouse.gif?t=1737062827\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260000/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737062827","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260000/page.bg.jpg?t=1737062827","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260000/a0fdf89854ea1e9d680f88ed1478cd3d730fea3a/capsul